---
title: Plum & Oyster-Glazed Pork Fillet with Ginger Rice, Snow Pea Salad & Crispy Shallots
description: A plum and oyster sauce needs some tender pork to really make those rich flavours shine. Add in a fragrant ginger rice to really bring a touch of something special to tonight’s dinner.

